    // exclude files defined in .gitignore\n        .pipe(gitignore())\n        .pipe(gulp.dest('dist'));\n});\n```\n\n\n## API\n\n### gitignore(file, [pattern],[options])\n\n#### file\n\nType: `string`\nDefault: `.gitignore`\n\nThe `.gitignore` file.\n\n#### pattern\n\nType: `array`\n\nYou can optionally pass an additional array of patterns to exlude from the stream.\n```js\ngitignore('.gitignore', ['foo', 'bar']);\n```\n\n#### options\n\nType: `object`\n\n##### options.dot\n\nType: `boolean`  \nDefault: `false`\n\nMatches files prefixed with a dot (eg. `.DS_Store`).\n\n\n## License\n\nMIT Â© [Thomas Lebeau](https://github.com/Thomas-Lebeau)\n","maintainers":[{"name":"thomaslebeau","email":"thomas@lebeau.io"}],"time":{"modified":"2015-09-06T17:41:42.819Z","created":"2015-09-06T17:41:42.819Z","0.1.0":"2015-09-06T17:41:42.819Z"},"homepage":"https://github.com/thomas-lebeau/gulp-gitignore#readme","keywords":["gulp","gulpplugin","git","gitignore","exclude","stream"],"repository":{"type":"git","url":"git+https://github.com/thomas-lebeau/gulp-gitignore.git"},"author":{"name":"Thomas Lebeau","email":"lebeau.thomas@gmail.com","url":"http://lebeau.io"},"bugs":{"url":"https://github.com/thomas-lebeau/gulp-gitignore/issues"},"license":"MIT","readmeFilename":"readme.md","_attachments":{}}